gomodel:SYNGO_4810  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 3a,b: HA-tagged InSyn1 was coexpressed in primary neuronal cells from mouse hippocampus with GPHN.FingR-GFP, a recombinant protein sensor of endogenous gephyrin (GPHN, a marker for inhibitory synapses) fused to green fluorescent protein (GFP). co-localization was ~60%.\n\nFigure 3c: InSyn1 coimmunoprecipitates with gephyrin (GPHN) when coexpressed in human embryonic kidney 293 (HEK293) cells.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Primary neuronal cultures from mouse hippocampus were prepared as described previously\"\n\nM&M: \"HA-InSyn1 (NM_176921)\" -->> confirms selected uniprot record" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
